992
01:21:32.262 --> 01:21:34.639
Bien, continue d'aboyer, Ruby.

993
01:21:48.904 --> 01:21:49.779
Par là.

994
01:21:59.789 --> 01:22:01.249
Attention à l'eau.

995
01:22:05.629 --> 01:22:07.047
Continue d'aboyer.

996
01:22:07.589 --> 01:22:08.757
Tiens bon.

997
01:22:20.894 --> 01:22:22.520
Daniel !

998
01:22:23.104 --> 01:22:25.315
- O'Neil, on est là.
- Il est vivant.

999
01:22:26.232 --> 01:22:30.070
Hypothermie, commotion possible.
Jambe cassée, blessures internes.

1000
01:22:30.153 --> 01:22:32.739
- On y va. On le sort de là.
- D'accord.

